  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/c1e225ebc93bc3d11bb124e6012b94e6.avif?t=1748485281\" width=628 height=106 /></span><br><br>The wicked Albert VII has captured Sami’s friend Vera and only you can help him save her! But it won’t be easy – you’ll need to roll, grapple, and jump to make it through in the colorful 3D world of <i>Super Sami Roll</i>.<br><br>Embark on a journey rolling through beautiful green fields, deserts dotted with magnificent pyramids, dangerous oozing volcanoes, frigid ice lands and many other memorable places with rolling physics and tons of hidden secrets!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/aa7bc2a5159e0e1977cdf6c05c102ae3.poster.avif?t=1748485281\" width=628 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/aa7bc2a5159e0e1977cdf6c05c102ae3.webm?t=1748485281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/aa7bc2a5159e0e1977cdf6c05c102ae3.mp4?t=1748485281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/18716d85138bff3732750510f6f7cb82.avif?t=1748485281\" width=628 height=106 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Beautiful World: </strong>Explore colorful, eye-catching environments, characters and enemies.<br></li><li> <strong>Level Variety: </strong>Play through dozens upon dozens of unique levels<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/cda935da26ed45b74e8548ce643ecf15.poster.avif?t=1748485281\" width=628 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/cda935da26ed45b74e8548ce643ecf15.webm?t=1748485281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/cda935da26ed45b74e8548ce643ecf15.mp4?t=1748485281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> <strong>2D & 3D Art: </strong>Features a combination of painstakingly hand-crafted pixel art and modern 3D graphics<br></li><li> <strong>Secret Hunting: </strong>Find tons of secrets – including awesome unlockable modes (even a multiplayer one!)<br></li><li> <strong>Challenges: </strong>Progressive difficulty that’s been fine-tuned to keep you engaged until you become a <i>true</i> master!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/b8d9c5800f3733e9fd7bf4f0ed5c162c.poster.avif?t=1748485281\" width=628 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/b8d9c5800f3733e9fd7bf4f0ed5c162c.webm?t=1748485281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/b8d9c5800f3733e9fd7bf4f0ed5c162c.mp4?t=1748485281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> <strong>Sami in Style: </strong>Customize your character.<br></li><li> <strong>Great Tunes: </strong>Upbeat soundtrack, check!<br><br><strong>It's time to ROLL!</strong></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/c1e225ebc93bc3d11bb124e6012b94e6.avif?t=1748485281\" width=628 height=106 /></span><br><br>The wicked Albert VII has captured Sami’s friend Vera and only you can help him save her! But it won’t be easy – you’ll need to roll, grapple, and jump to make it through in the colorful 3D world of <i>Super Sami Roll</i>.<br><br>Embark on a journey rolling through beautiful green fields, deserts dotted with magnificent pyramids, dangerous oozing volcanoes, frigid ice lands and many other memorable places with rolling physics and tons of hidden secrets!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/aa7bc2a5159e0e1977cdf6c05c102ae3.poster.avif?t=1748485281\" width=628 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/aa7bc2a5159e0e1977cdf6c05c102ae3.webm?t=1748485281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/aa7bc2a5159e0e1977cdf6c05c102ae3.mp4?t=1748485281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/18716d85138bff3732750510f6f7cb82.avif?t=1748485281\" width=628 height=106 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>Beautiful World: </strong>Explore colorful, eye-catching environments, characters and enemies.<br></li><li> <strong>Level Variety: </strong>Play through dozens upon dozens of unique levels<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/cda935da26ed45b74e8548ce643ecf15.poster.avif?t=1748485281\" width=628 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/cda935da26ed45b74e8548ce643ecf15.webm?t=1748485281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/cda935da26ed45b74e8548ce643ecf15.mp4?t=1748485281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> <strong>2D & 3D Art: </strong>Features a combination of painstakingly hand-crafted pixel art and modern 3D graphics<br></li><li> <strong>Secret Hunting: </strong>Find tons of secrets – including awesome unlockable modes (even a multiplayer one!)<br></li><li> <strong>Challenges: </strong>Progressive difficulty that’s been fine-tuned to keep you engaged until you become a <i>true</i> master!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/b8d9c5800f3733e9fd7bf4f0ed5c162c.poster.avif?t=1748485281\" width=628 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/b8d9c5800f3733e9fd7bf4f0ed5c162c.webm?t=1748485281\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554640/extras/b8d9c5800f3733e9fd7bf4f0ed5c162c.mp4?t=1748485281\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> <strong>Sami in Style: </strong>Customize your character.<br></li><li> <strong>Great Tunes: </strong>Upbeat soundtrack, check!<br><br><strong>It's time to ROLL!</strong></li></ul>",
